{"tid":1843693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★王永平：難以理解\" 政府完全封關不可行\"    可能引發更大的政治風暴","createTime":"2020-01-26T10:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T16:46:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5280dc298d77f7ed17b43d07b6b69d24a326f3e","tid":1843693,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】食物及衞生局局長重申，本港完全封關不可行，會考慮加強入境管制，包括檢視縮短通關時間。公務員事務局前局長王永平批評，香港遲遲未有限制內地人入境，等於把病毒從源頭引入。<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒從內地擴散，本港關口檢疫成為焦點。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，目前在機場和高鐵站試行電子健康申報，日後會考慮在其他口岸實施。<br />\n<br />\n本港早前亦與廣東省簽署聯防聯控協議，體溫過高人士不能出境，本港亦會檢視縮短關口通關時間。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n政府再三強調完全封關不切實際，公務員事務局前局長王永平形容難以理解。他認為應及時堵截疫症源頭，減少內地染病人士入境，否則醫護人員和市民不滿，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可能引發更大的政治風暴</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378182&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGeoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=6bbb6165\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378182&h=938e41da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378182</a>"},{"pid":"5d2f0af9ccdc240896d695c8a0fcc588d43222cb","tid":1843693,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b26d56a87604253d0b88f774388e316ca6e6c95","tid":1843693,"uid":53238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:13:36.000Z","msg":"本身以為係想引入疫症再扮盡力抗疫搶分<br />\n點知佢又真係 hea 做連藍絲都唔妥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=